WEBVTT

00:00.240 --> 00:01.741
<i>Previously on "Heartland":</i>

00:01.776 --> 00:03.743
My "Mom's the Word" blog,
they want to publish it!

00:03.778 --> 00:06.312
A book tour?

00:06.380 --> 00:07.880
<i>Adrian, take charge!</i>

00:07.914 --> 00:09.434
<i>His breeder
said he's a problem.</i>

00:09.449 --> 00:11.750
<i>If you're not
up for the job...</i>

00:11.818 --> 00:14.153
I know somebody who might be.

00:14.221 --> 00:16.622
<i>I'd like you to work with Zeus.</i>

00:16.657 --> 00:18.991
<i>Amy, with Zeus on her own?</i>

00:24.263 --> 00:25.463
- Hey.
- Ty?!

00:25.531 --> 00:27.900
Adrian...

00:27.934 --> 00:28.901
It was Adrian
in the stable that night.

00:28.935 --> 00:30.402
I saw him running away!

00:32.604 --> 00:34.673
You have the greenest eyes.

00:36.000 --> 00:42.074
